thread.title: Police dash-cam video shows Michigan State Police trooper, suspect falling from highway overpass after chase in Saginaw County
thread.title_full: Police dash-cam video shows Michigan State Police trooper, suspect falling from highway overpass after chase in Saginaw County

author: Brad Devereaux | bdeverea@mlive.com
title: Police dash-cam video shows Michigan State Police trooper, suspect falling from highway overpass after chase in Saginaw County
text: A Saginaw Township Police Department cruiser's dash camera captured the moment when a Michigan State Police trooper and a suspect in a vehicle chase fell from a highway overpass in Saginaw County.
